trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot"></xref> objects inside an <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap"></xref> control.

trans-unit.source: The HotSpotCollection class represents a collection that enables an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageMap> control to maintain a list of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.HotSpot> objects it contains.
